STATE of Iowa, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Katrina Nikole COOPER, Defendant-Appellant. No. 18-0651 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 9, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Katrina Nikole Cooper appeals a judgment and sentence for delivery of more than five grams of methamphetamine. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
